{"tid":1703591,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"監警會主席梁定邦認同國際專家小組指監警會權力不足的評論","createTime":"2019-11-10T10:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T12:12:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7b68378eec59d1e140a150d06ffcfe9fc4885dbd","tid":1703591,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:52:55.000Z","msg":"監警會國際專家小組成員發表聲明，認為監警會的權力及獨立調查能力，不足以應付近期的事件，建議由獨立機構進行調查。監警會主席梁定邦表示，同意專家小組意見，但指出發表報告是希望讓政府及外界考慮下一步工作。政府發言人回覆說，今次審視旨在查找事實，找出未來方向，政府將密切關注審視結果，仔細研究所有建議。<br />\n<br />\n2019-11-10 18:42:02"},{"pid":"1b36b7749c42c822bbef710bfcc7538feb921c14","tid":1703591,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母<br />\n阻9交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出泥<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fa31906ae857e07cc949df4843155c1015f81da","tid":1703591,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b36b7749c42c822bbef710bfcc7538feb921c14","tid":1703591,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:53:27.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母<br />\n阻9交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出泥<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:53:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f676e8c9fb43f81d4b32d2ab427a14fc2237f09a","tid":1703591,"uid":96540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2296014c6df6217d2a96a415602aca25609ab3fd","tid":1703591,"uid":170244,"like":10,"dislike":0,"scor